Boot Manager
============

Boot Manager is boot loader editor of Pardus Linux


Requirements
------------

* python-grub (in trunk/python-modules)


Installing & Running
--------------------

1. Add comar/model.xml to /etc/comar/model.xml
2. Restart COMAR
3. Edit comar/system.boot.py and set GRUB_CONF
4. Run: hav register System.Boot grub comar/system.boot.py
5. Run: ./boot-manager.py
